  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028610/extras/20928aa8fdff104be862b9cac60b93be.avif?t=1727542906\" width=614 height=100 /></span><br><br>World of Paintball is a sports simulator based on the real-life sport called paintball!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modes</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Team Deathmatch</li><li>Best player</li><li>Target Elimination</li><li>Classic paintball game mode</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Weapons</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Large selection of different weapons for the game, both automatic and pistols!</li><li>We even have grenades!</li><li>Huge selection of different skins for weapons, from common to the rarest!</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028610/extras/c566ec5a3d9a347cb7389fb578c9015a.poster.avif?t=1727542906\" width=615 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028610/extras/c566ec5a3d9a347cb7389fb578c9015a.webm?t=1727542906\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Locations</h2>Wide selection of maps from different locations!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028610/extras/92f4b3912a35cebdcb08769471ff388e.avif?t=1727542906\" width=614 height=312 /></span><br><br>A good strategy and great team play will help you win!<br>Invite your friends and take first place!",
